%header.subhead
  %h1 Digital Tv Guide
  %p.lead
    When does the next episode of house airs? Homeland was cool, wat other serie could I watch? Digital TV guide will help you with that. 
  %ul.nav.tabs
    %li= link_to 'Total serie overview', ''
    %li= link_to 'Create your own guide', ''
%section#guides  
  %ul.thumbnails
    - 2.times do      
      - %w(hot must_see new user).shuffle.each do |group|
        %li.span6
          .thumbnail
            = image_tag "#{group}_1_block.jpeg", :width => 460
%section#activity
  .page-header
    %h2 Just aired
  %ul.thumbnails
    - 5.times do 
      - %w(hot_1_block.jpeg hot_2_block.jpeg user_1_block.jpeg user_2_block.jpeg).each do |image_name|
        %li.span3
          .thumbnail
            = image_tag image_name, size: '210x150'
            %h5 
              Program name
              %small
                Just a title
            %dl
              %dt Watched 
              %dd x times
              %dt Hotness 
              %dd very nasty
            
